OL,3,CMum and two children killed in crash
OL,4,Cwith bus, inquest hears
OL,6,FThree members of a Ukrainian refugee
OL,7,Ffamily died in a head-on crash with a
OL,8,Fdouble decker bus, an inquest has
OL,9,Fheard.
OL,11,FDaria Bartienieva, 35, died along with
OL,12,Fher six-year-old son, Ihor, and
OL,13,Fstepdaughter, Anastasiia, 15, when
OL,14,Ftheir car collided with the bus on the
OL,15,FA61 between Ripon and Harrogate in
OL,16,FNorth Yorkshire.
