OL,3,CMum and two children killed in crash
OL,4,Cwith bus, inquest hears
OL,6,FAn inquest heard "glare from the sun
OL,7,For a distraction in the car" may have
OL,8,Fcaused Ms Bartienieva to cross into
OL,9,Fthe opposite carriageway and hit the
OL,10,Ffront of a bus.
OL,12,FCoroner Jonathan Leach said Ms
OL,13,FBartienieva failed to negotiate a bend
OL,14,Fas she passed through the village of
OL,15,FSouth Stainley, near Ripley,
