OL,3,CMum and two children killed in crash
OL,4,Cwith bus, inquest hears
OL,6,FThe inquest heard five people on the
OL,7,Fbus were injured, including the
OL,8,Fdriver. Ms Bartienieva's Vauxhall
OL,9,FMeriva was pushed back into her lane
OL,10,Fby the impact of the crash, causing it
OL,11,Fto collide with a Toyota Aygo which
OL,12,Fwas travelling behind her.
OL,14,FShe and the two children died at the
OL,15,Fscene of the crash on September 3 2023.
OL,17,FEmma Faith, who was on the 36 bus with
OL,18,Fher mother after having lunch in
OL,19,FHarrogate, said she saw a silver car
OL,20,Fgoing into their side "on the wrong
OL,21,Fside of the road".
