OL,3,CMum and two children killed in crash
OL,4,Cwith bus, inquest hears
OL,6,FIn a statement read by Mr Leach, Ms
OL,7,FFaith said: "The impact was deafening.
OL,8,FThere was an almighty bang and the car
OL,9,Fhit us ... The next thing I remember
OL,10,Fis trying to figure out why I was on
OL,11,Fthe floor."
OL,13,FLorraine Gayle, who was driving the
OL,14,FToyota Aygo, said Ms Bartienieva's car
OL,15,Fhad a green "P" sticker on the back,
OL,16,Findicating a newly-qualified driver.
OL,18,FHer statement read: "As an experienced
OL,19,Fdriver, I was giving her more time and
OL,20,Fspace."
