OL,3,CMum and two children killed in crash
OL,4,Cwith bus, inquest hears
OL,6,FMs Gayle described seeing Ms
OL,7,FBartienieva's car "hitting the bus
OL,8,Fvirtually head-on".
OL,10,FMs Bartienieva's other daughter, 15-
OL,11,Fyear-old Liza, was not involved in the
OL,12,Fincident. Almost #50,000 was raised to
OL,13,Fsupport her after the collision.
OL,15,FIn a statement she said her mother did
OL,16,Faccountancy work in Ukraine before
OL,17,Fmoving to the UK in June 2022 because
OL,18,Fof the Russian invasion.
