OL,3,CMum and two children killed in crash
OL,4,Cwith bus, inquest hears
OL,6,FThe girl said they lived with a host
OL,7,Ffamily in Ripon and "settled into the
OL,8,Fcommunity".
OL,10,FShe said Ms Bartienieva's husband died
OL,11,Fthree months before the crash.
OL,13,FThe girl said her mother had a driving
OL,14,Flicence in Ukraine and had bought a
OL,15,Fcar in Leeds in August 2022, asking a
OL,16,Ffamily friend to take her around the
OL,17,Flocal roads and small towns to
OL,18,Ffamiliarise herself with them.
