OL,3,CMum and two children killed in crash
OL,4,Cwith bus, inquest hears
OL,6,FShe said by the time the crash
OL,7,Fhappened Ms Bartienieva had been
OL,8,Fdriving in the UK for about a year,
OL,9,Fwas a "considerate driver" and "very
OL,10,Ffamiliar" with that stretch of road.
OL,12,FNorth Yorkshire Police traffic
OL,13,Fsergeant Ken Riley, who investigated
OL,14,Fthe crash, said it was caused by Ms
OL,15,FBartienieva driving into the opposite
OL,16,Fcarriageway.
OL,18,FHe told the inquest the reason for
OL,19,Fthis is not known, but "glare from the
OL,20,Fsun is a consideration, as is a
OL,21,Fdistraction within the vehicle".
